Trng sinh n cp ba thi k Dng i cn khng ti kp cao hng lin b vi v tin vo Thm Vc bn trong.y l mt ci tin thn ti hin, yu ma n lc phm nhn th gii!Thn Thoi thc tnh, ng thc vt ha thnh yu ma, d gii qu qui xm ln, thn l a Cu cha t nhn loi a v trn ngp nguy him, m lc ny thn b Thm Vc dng game gi lp phng thc bung xung a Cu, mang cho nhn loi hi vng.Dng i tin vo Thm Vc thu hoch c chng khng hn phch nng lc, cn c hn mn pht dc l nim, hn mun lm mt v ng hn triu hon s, chun b trc t xy mt nhnh hn phch i qun, li thm d Thm Vc.Thin t v song, tung honh vng triu tuyt i thin kiu!Ba bi tn ph nhn gian, yu uy thao thin ci th Yu Vng!Mt tay che tri, honh p chnh o Ma o t s!Lm Dng i hn phch i qun xut hin cng ngy cng nhiu lnh lng gii chng sinh khip s khng b tn v sau, hn cng thu c uy chn lng gii tn xng.Hn Chu!**Cnh gii: T Kh, Tm Ton, Linh Chiu, Khng V, Luyn Hn. . .
